title: #399 SummerHouse: Kate Casey Crossover Episode!
description:
Here's something interesting for your Friday: we did a crossover with Kate Casey of "Reality Life with Kate Casey." Basically, we went to her studio, and we talked "Summer House," but also "Bachelor," "Southern Charm," "Vanderpump Rules," and more. And because we didn't get to cover everything we wanted on "Summer House," Ronnie and Ben circled back at the end to talk about the show for an extra 25 minutes! Hope you enjoy!

00:00:00 - Intro / Kate Casey crossover fun times
01:01:06 - Summer House extra content
